National Gallery Web Site Mailing List

   TO SUBSCRIBE
   Sign up for our Web site mailing list by sending an e-mail to
   maillist@nga.gov and leave the subject field blank. Every month we will
   send you a list of several items that are new on our Web site. We will
   also point out noteworthy features that you may have missed on your
   previous visits.

   Your message must come from the e-mail account to which you want the
   updates to be sent.

   TO CONTACT US
   Please note that the return e-mail address on this message is a
   send-only address. Questions and comments to this address will not
   receive a reply. If you would like to contact us, please write to
   webfeedback@nga.gov.

   TO CHANGE YOUR ADDRESS
   First send e-mail from your old address to maillist@nga.gov and type
   the word remove in the subject field. Then, re-subscribe to the list
   from your new address by sending e-mail to maillist@nga.gov and leave
   the subject field blank.

   TO UNSUBSCRIBE
   If you would like to remove your name from this list, send e-mail to
   maillist@nga.gov and type the word remove in the subject field.

   We look forward to hearing from you.

